revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yeboahs}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yeboah'' is the 17142<sup>nd</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1653 individuals. ''Yeboah'' is most common among Black/African American (96.49%) individuals.
